<section class="hero"><div class="container">
<p class="eyebrow">Independent local information</p>
<h1>Understand a wildlife problem before choosing a provider</h1>
<p class="lead">Clear Calgary-focused guides about animals in attics, raccoons, squirrels, bats, skunks, birds, warning signs, prevention, and what to ask a local wildlife professional.</p>
<div class="actions"><a class="primary-button" href="tel:+15870000000">Call (587) 000-0000</a><a class="secondary-button" href="/contact.html">Request a callback</a></div>
<p class="trust-note">We do not perform wildlife-control work. Requests may be shared with independent local providers.</p>
</div></section>
<section class="section"><div class="container"><h2>Start with the problem you noticed</h2><div class="grid">
<div class="card"><h3>Animal in the attic</h3><p>Scratching, movement, droppings, odors, or damaged vents may point to an attic entry.</p><a href="/services/animal-in-attic-calgary.html">See common signs</a></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Raccoon activity</h3><p>Learn about nighttime noise, roof damage, denning behaviour, and why young animals change the removal plan.</p><a href="/services/raccoon-removal-calgary.html">Raccoon guide</a></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Bat activity</h3><p>Learn why timing and species protection matter and why direct handling should be avoided.</p><a href="/services/bat-removal-calgary.html">Bat guide</a></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Squirrel activity</h3><p>Review common roofline entry points, daytime sounds, chewing concerns, and prevention steps.</p><a href="/services/squirrel-removal-calgary.html">Squirrel guide</a></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Skunks under a structure</h3><p>Understand burrows, odor, pets, and safe next steps for a den beneath a deck or shed.</p><a href="/services/skunk-removal-calgary.html">Skunk guide</a></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Birds in vents or chimneys</h3><p>Learn about nesting material, blocked airflow, seasonal restrictions, and exclusion.</p><a href="/services/bird-removal-calgary.html">Bird guide</a></div>
</div></div></section>
<section class="section alt"><div class="container two-col"><article class="content">
<h2>How this website works</h2>
<ol><li>Read a guide and identify the signs you are seeing.</li><li>Call or submit the contact form.</li><li>Your request may be sent to an independent provider serving Calgary.</li><li>The provider explains its own availability, inspection process, pricing, and terms.</li></ol>
<div class="notice"><strong>No surprise price promises:</strong> We do not publish fixed prices because every property, animal, entry point, and repair need is different. Ask the provider for a written scope and estimate.</div>
</article><aside><h2>Useful questions to ask</h2><ul><li>How will the animal be identified?</li><li>Are young animals likely present?</li><li>What exclusion and repair work is included?</li><li>Is follow-up included?</li><li>What written warranty applies?</li></ul></aside></div></section>
<section class="section"><div class="container"><h2>Popular learning guides</h2><div class="grid">
<div class="card"><h3>Scratching in the ceiling</h3><p>Time of day and sound type can help narrow down the likely animal.</p><a href="/learning-center/why-am-i-hearing-scratching-in-my-ceiling.html">Read the guide</a></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Raccoon attic signs</h3><p>Heavy nighttime movement, damaged vents, odor, and droppings are common clues.</p><a href="/learning-center/signs-of-raccoons-in-attic.html">Read the guide</a></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Wildlife-removal cost factors</h3><p>Learn what usually affects a quote without relying on a misleading fixed price.</p><a href="/guides/wildlife-removal-cost-calgary.html">Read the cost guide</a></div>
</div></div></section>
</main>
