    <p class="disclaimer"><strong>Important:</strong> Calgary Wildlife Help is not a wildlife-control contractor and does not perform inspections, removals, repairs, or emergency services. We provide general educational information and may connect visitors with independent third-party providers. Providers set their own availability, prices, methods, warranties, and service terms. Do not approach or handle wildlife. For immediate danger, suspected rabies exposure, or a medical emergency, contact the appropriate public authority or emergency service.</p>
